.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, lemonade, milk, mirinda
There 5 different types of food: apricot, broccoli, lettuce, orange, watermelon
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, blend, prince, siglo, swisher
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, skateboarding, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person eating apricot##2
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 8. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
12. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
13. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | milk       | mirinda       | almond-milk   | lemonade      | juice    |
| Food       | watermelon | orange        | apricot       | lettuce       | broccoli |
| Cigar        | swisher     | blend        | siglo | vegafina        | prince  |
| Sport      | volleyball | skateboarding | climbing      | weightlifting | parkour  |

